# Moderation and privacy boundaries

This app can take moderation actions, send modmail, summarize content, update flairs, and call moderator-configured AI providers.

Preserve the documented safety model:

- Safe mode defaults on.
- Live removal requires moderator opt-in with safe mode off.
- Redis audit logs record proposed and completed actions.
- Redis idempotency prevents duplicate trigger actions.

Do not copy subreddit-specific secrets, moderation policy, or API credentials into reusable templates.
When changing user-facing moderation behavior, keep auditability and duplicate prevention intact.
